data.description: Welcome! This stunning ranch style home has a FULL finished basement and is located in a well established neighborhood. It sits in a cul-de-sac. This home features 4 bedrooms plus a bonus room and 3 full baths. Hardwood floors throughout the main level living area with carpet in the bedrooms. Newer roof, water softener, and AC unit. 2 car garage with a side entry. Oversized yard that is level and backs up to trees. Schedule your showing today.
